descriptionHtml:
The latest version of MyBluebird comes with innovative features that bring more comfort, convenience, and benefits to every ride. With EZPoint, the more transactions you make, the more rewards you get — from promos and discounts to exclusive offers.

Top Features:

1. EZPay – Cashless Payments from Anywhere
Ride from anywhere and pay cashless. Even if you’re already inside the taxi and want to switch to cashless, you can! Just use EZPay. With EZPay, there’s no need to prepare cash or worry about payments. Enter the taxi number through the EZPay feature in the MyBluebird app. Pay cashless using digital wallets and enjoy available promos or discounts for a more affordable ride.

2. All-In-One Services
MyBluebird offers a complete transport solution in one platform to meet all your travel needs:

Taxi: Comfortable and safe Bluebird and Silverbird executive taxis for your daily commutes. Premium fleet like Toyota Alphard also available.

Goldenbird Car Rental: A flexible option for business or leisure travel, now with electric vehicle (EV) fleets such as BYD, Denza, and Hyundai IONIQ.

Delivery: Send documents or important packages safely and quickly via Bluebird Kirim.

Shuttle Service: Efficient and practical shuttle solutions for better mobility.

3. Multi-Payment – Cash & Cashless Options
MyBluebird lets you choose the most convenient payment method. Cash is still accepted, but you can also go cashless using credit cards, eVouchers, Trip Vouchers, GoPay, ShopeePay, LinkAja, DANA, i.saku, and OVO. With so many options, your transaction experience becomes smoother and simpler.

4. EZPoint – The More You Ride, the More You Earn
With the EZPoint loyalty program, every transaction earns you points that can be redeemed for exciting rewards like ride discounts, special promos, concert tickets, hotel stays, and exclusive gifts.

5. Promos – Save More with Special Offers
Enjoy a variety of attractive promo codes, exclusive discounts, and cashback deals that make your rides more affordable. Always check for the latest promos to maximize your savings.

6. Subscription – Ride More, Save More
With a subscription plan, your rides become more cost-efficient and practical! Enjoy recurring discounts and other perks based on your selected travel package.

7. Fixed Price – Transparent Fares from the Start
No more fare guessing. You'll know the exact price upfront at the time of booking, ensuring a more comfortable, secure, and transparent journey.

8. Chat to Driver – Easier Communication
Communicating with your driver is now more convenient. Use the Chat to Driver feature to send messages directly from the app — share your location, provide extra instructions, or check your ride status easily.

9. Advance Booking – Plan Your Ride Ahead of Time
Schedule your ride in advance for more flexible and convenient travel planning. This feature lets you book a vehicle ahead of time to match your schedule perfectly.

Install MyBluebird now and book a ride with complete and trusted transport solutions. Whether it’s a taxi ride, car rental, shuttle service, delivery, or ride hailing, everything is available in one app. Make payments easily with EZPay, collect points with EZPoint, and enjoy exclusive promos for safer, more comfortable, and more rewarding journeys.

Visit: bluebirdgroup.com for more information.
